  "body": "Since there now exists a [apis repo](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-apis), this is an opportune time to begin fleshing out a barebones provider. Should perform type validations and proper error handling out of the gate. I'd like to aim for it to be more of a wrapper, at the beginning. Perhaps something that can be imported to ethers or web3.js.\r\n\r\n@ricmoo - do you have any thoughts?",
